Package: cat.stack
Title: General-Purpose LLM Text Classification Engine
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: person("Chris", "Soria", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "chrissoria@berkeley.edu")
Description: R interface to the Python cat-stack package. General-purpose text,
    image, and PDF classification using LLMs with no domain assumptions. The base
    engine for the CatLLM ecosystem.
